      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, I'm confused. You first said the competition drives down wages, but then you said it raises them and that the evidence is \"clear.\" That sounds like a contradiction. If there's a consensus that it's a \"boon,\" then why do so many economists and politicians argue that it's a net negative for local communities? Isn't the impact on wages one of the most contested parts of the whole debate?",
